+                                        <span class="answer" id="answer_147">
+
+                                            <div class="bug_answer_title">
+                                                
+                                                <strong>Do performance testing</strong>
+                                            </div>
+                                            <p>I'd love to know what pages on the site execute slowly. Feel free to experiment a bit with the public site, or to download the code and try locally.</p>
+
+<p>Once you've done that, tell us what we need to optimize, or send a patch in that makes us use Django caching more aggressively!</p>
